_sText:
Installation:
Open file using WinRar (You can download WinRar at http://www.rarlab.com/) and extract the BSP file into
C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\<YOURUSER>\Counter-Strike: Source\CStrike\Maps

Then run Counter-Strike: Source and create your server, the map should now be in your map list, if not go to
the console and type in 'map de_dev_city' and the next time you run a server it should be in the map list.



Map was made by Chap1400, Any Custom Textures were made by Chris Chapman (And a special thanks to him!)

You can email me at: chap1410@googlemail.com

Thanks for downloading and enjoy!
